{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1839, "height": 2490, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "孝妇张氏李氏传杜含章", "block_bbox": [192, 224, 732, 268], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "孝妇张李氏者，增生思义之妻，庠生宏勋、廪生力行之母也。", "block_bbox": [264, 281, 1275, 322], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "年十五归张，时翁已弃养，惟姑在堂。氏一以承颜愉志为务。姑有女，家贫，氏窥姑心欲周之也，每躬亲劳苦，曲求微资以给之。\n", "block_bbox": [187, 336, 1530, 433], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "乾隆丁卯，氏夫赴乡试。场事未毕而姑得瘫病，水浆不入口者数日。氏百计莫施，呼天哀痛曰：“与其殆姑，毋宁自殒。古有以死代君父者，天宁不许我代姑耶?”长跪哭祷，夜以继日，目为之肿。\n", "block_bbox": [185, 447, 1531, 600], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "越两昼夜，姑就寝，氏坐侍室隅，恍惚若寐，见一丈夫衣冠甚伟，向氏言曰：“汝姑本不起，念汝孝，特为尔医之。”于是，取药数丸置姑口中而去。氏惊觉，视姑睡方熟。未几，姑醒，手足忽能举动，自是病日减，能自起立。后十日，氏夫场峻而归，省母毕，氏白其事。思义曰：“尔时，吾在汴城，心跳不宁，夜得一梦，亦如汝所云，殆有神佑乎?”于是，焚香具奠，拜神惠焉。", "block_bbox": [184, 615, 1534, 879], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "氏自姑病后，常以姑苦寒，秋冬每与同寝，历十五年，姑年七十以他病终。氏与夫营葬事，以弟思忠贫，衣衾棺椁自竭己资，不强弟之所无。氏之友，亦氏之孝也。\n", "block_bbox": [187, 894, 1533, 1044], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜含章曰：盖闻百行莫大于孝，而求之巾帼中为难。今观张李氏之以身代姑，情意肫挚，可谓纯孝矣。梦授药医事，近诞，然“孝悌之至，通乎神明”，古语岂欺我哉？\n", "block_bbox": [187, 1060, 1534, 1211], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "卷十一艺文·传杜含章传张文煜", "block_bbox": [188, 1224, 1194, 1268], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜含章字子贞，友白之季子也。为文沉著朴茂。乾隆乙亥房元。性醇笃，邃于经子。所著《<四书>述要》《<书经>句解》，皆能发明先圣奥旨。至《天文志》《地理图》《律吕精义》《皇极经世》诸书，类能入室窥奥。授引后，教因才施。渑、郏、新邑声价之士，半出其门。及司铎考城，启迪士子径而不迂。学者称为“韶峰先生”云。\n", "block_bbox": [186, 1280, 1535, 1544], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "卷十七人物·儒林", "block_bbox": [189, 1556, 526, 1596], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜含章：张村人，乾隆举人，字子贞，性醇正，笃于学。天文、地理、律吕、星象，无不淹贯。著有《易经句解》《书经句解》《四书述要》，待梓。", "block_bbox": [191, 1610, 1532, 1713], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "卷十八人物·节孝", "block_bbox": [192, 1723, 528, 1764], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "节孝总坊：侯氏，杜良田妻；张氏，杜兰玉妻；李氏，杜廷彦妻；杜氏，贺三重妻；张氏，杜星五妻；杜氏，薛发荣妻。\n", "block_bbox": [192, 1777, 1531, 1878], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "节妇未入祠者：杜氏，王三重妻；杜氏，崔如岳妻；杜氏，张荫桐妻，守节四十年；庞氏，杜鸿筠妻，廿一夫亡，苦守。\n", "block_bbox": [192, 1891, 1532, 1989], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "烈妇：杜氏，庠生王熙妻。夫亡，七日不食，殡夫前一日自缢于灵前。督宪旌曰：“殉夫就义”。\n", "block_bbox": [190, 2003, 1535, 2107], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "卷十九人物·乡宾", "block_bbox": [194, 2119, 535, 2159], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜万益，坻坞人，年九十；杜云河，坻坞人，年九十；杜青连，谢（“谢”为“窑”之误）湾人，年八十一。\n", "block_bbox": [193, 2172, 1535, 2275], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1634, 666, 1703, 1294], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "三九四", "block_bbox": [1643, 1884, 1688, 1989], "block_id": 18, "block_order": null}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9300525188446045, "coordinate": [184.17742919921875, 615.47021484375, 1534.116943359375, 879.517333984375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.923022985458374, "coordinate": [186.29193115234375, 1280.012939453125, 1535.47509765625, 1544.203857421875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9063505530357361, "coordinate": [185.99700927734375, 447.66192626953125, 1531.51904296875, 600.6010131835938]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9028719663619995, "coordinate": [187.88946533203125, 1060.748291015625, 1534.023681640625, 1211.537353515625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9028229117393494, "coordinate": [187.00897216796875, 894.5120849609375, 1533.33642578125, 1044.8026123046875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8952641487121582, "coordinate": [192.3349609375, 1891.083251953125, 1532.8017578125, 1989.790283203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8795337677001953, "coordinate": [192.05035400390625, 1777.94287109375, 1531.81591796875, 1878.302734375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8789517283439636, "coordinate": [193.5443115234375, 2172.033203125, 1535.4754638671875, 2275.0390625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8703734278678894, "coordinate": [190.61474609375, 2003.5810546875, 1535.2596435546875, 2107.30322265625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8685752153396606, "coordinate": [187.0595703125, 336.5762023925781, 1530.6064453125, 433.7315368652344]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8614986538887024, "coordinate": [191.4859619140625, 1610.702880859375, 1532.758544921875, 1713.576416015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8068521022796631, "coordinate": [264.4163818359375, 281.0586853027344, 1275.6741943359375, 322.7514953613281]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7766381502151489, "coordinate": [192.07485961914062, 1723.8638916015625, 528.4951171875, 1764.7674560546875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7346203327178955, "coordinate": [189.9832305908203, 1556.4072265625, 526.0087280273438, 1596.66796875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.6964626312255859, 